verses:
There are 20 yogas named after the
different figures they represent and coming under the
general designation of आकृतियोग (Akriti yoga). They are
(1) खूप (Yupa), a sacrificial post; (2) इषु (Ishu), an arrow;
(3) पाकि (Sakti), a spear; (4) यत्र (Yava), a barleycorn;

If a person be born in the first quarter
of the star Aslesha, there is no dinger to any person ;
if in the 2nd quarter, there is the risk of losing money ;
if in the 3rd quarter, his mother runs the risk of losing
her life; if in the 4th quarter the father runs a similar
risk.
